        <name>emul_espi_api_set_vw</name>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Passes eSPI virtual wires set request (virtual wire packet) to the emulator. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>The emulator updates the state (level) of its virtual wire.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>target</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
